might still be here among us?

105
00:06:12,291 --> 00:06:14,041
Hurry up and catch
'em, then, copper!

106
00:06:14,125 --> 00:06:15,583
I can't believe such
a horrible thing

107
00:06:15,666 --> 00:06:18,250
could ever happen at our
quiet little inn, sir!

108
00:06:18,333 --> 00:06:20,208
[TANAKA grunts]

109
00:06:20,291 --> 00:06:22,083
Everyone, just remain calm.

110
00:06:22,166 --> 00:06:23,791
