You're the killer!

115
00:06:33,708 --> 00:06:34,666
That's the answer. I know it!

116
00:06:34,750 --> 00:06:35,875
[TANAKA]
No! You've got it all wrong!

117
00:06:35,958 --> 00:06:38,083
Popuko. Don't be rude
to the guests, now.

118
00:06:38,166 --> 00:06:39,750
Whaddaya mean?

119
00:06:43,791 --> 00:06:45,458
Did you stop in on your
way home from work?

120
00:06:45,541 --> 00:06:46,666
[TANAKA]
Oh, yes.

121
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:48,416
Or were you on your way
home from a murder?

122
00:06:48,500 --> 00:06:51,750
Hey, don't interfere with
my investigation, lady!

123
00:06:51,833 --> 00:06:53,666
On the rocks? Splash of water?

124
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:55,083
Or a splash of murder?

125
00:06:55,166 --> 00:06:57,125
You moron!

126
00:07:02,625 --> 00:07:06,416
Okay, what have you got to
share with me, forensics? Huh?

127
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:09,125
[PIPIMI] So what was the
murder weapon, then, love?

128
00:07:09,208 --> 00:07:11,250
Well, uh, some
kinda blunt object.

129
00:07:11,333 --> 00:07:13,166
It only took one blow.

130
00:07:13,250 --> 00:07:17,416
