134
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:31,041
you're the number one
busybody in Ginza.

135
00:07:31,125 --> 00:07:32,708
[sighs, chuckles]

136
00:07:32,791 --> 00:07:36,000
Sure am. Thanks for the
compliment, Popuko.

137
00:07:36,083 --> 00:07:39,083
Now, we should get to work.
There's so much to figure out!

138
00:07:39,166 --> 00:07:40,791
Yes, ma'am!

139
00:07:40,875 --> 00:07:42,666
[PIPIMI] The killer is
still at large in the inn.

140
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:44,708
We need to gather as much
evidence as possible.

141
00:07:44,791 --> 00:07:46,541
[POPUKO]
The basic rule of detective work

142
00:07:46,625 --> 00:07:48,875
is thorough data gathering!

143
00:07:48,958 --> 00:07:51,208
I recall that my late
husband used to get up

144
00:07:51,291 --> 00:07:53,666
so many damn times
in the middle of the night

145
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:56,583
because he had to go
pee, or so he claimed.

146
00:07:56,666 --> 00:07:57,958
