147
00:07:58,041 --> 00:08:00,208
Popuko! Assemble all of
the guests and staff.

148
00:08:00,291 --> 00:08:01,416
I've figured it out!

149
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:03,208
[PIPIMI whispering]

150
00:08:03,291 --> 00:08:05,416
Oh. Oh, oh. Oh!

151
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:08,791
No kidding! I totally get
what you're saying now!

152
00:08:14,583 --> 00:08:17,041
Mama! Everyone's assembled!

153
00:08:17,125 --> 00:08:19,208
Popuko. Thanks for your help.

154
00:08:19,291 --> 00:08:21,875
So, um, why did
you bring us here?

155
00:08:21,958 --> 00:08:24,708
Don't tell me. You know
who the killer is? Tell me!

156
00:08:24,791 --> 00:08:27,250
Uh, well, I didn't
do it. I swear!

157
00:08:27,333 --> 00:08:31,166
Now, now, quiet down.
Nobody needs to get too excited.

158
00:08:34,791 --> 00:08:37,750
I started working in Ginza
a very long time ago,

159
00:08:37,833 --> 00:08:41,000
