in those days,

161
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:44,583
the world seemed so
fresh and dazzling,

162
00:08:44,666 --> 00:08:46,208
a feast for my senses.

163
00:08:46,291 --> 00:08:48,416
I accepted Ginza at face value,

164
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:52,458
and Ginza accepted me in return,
without question or expectation.

165
00:08:52,541 --> 00:08:54,041
