It's me, Sosogu Hoshifuri!

426
00:23:40,208 --> 00:23:41,166
Oh, no!

427
00:23:41,250 --> 00:23:43,041
Daichi wants to
find his true self,

428
00:23:43,125 --> 00:23:45,541
so he's planning to
study abroad for a while.

429
00:23:45,625 --> 00:23:47,041
We're going to have to be apart!

